00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:13.480
No, but that's a great thing.

00:24:13.480 --> 00:24:16.040
The worst thing--

00:24:16.040 --> 00:24:16.520
I don't know.

00:24:16.520 --> 00:24:25.340
I mean, I feel like you're
suspended in adolescence,

00:24:25.340 --> 00:24:29.080
