00:30:44.220 --> 00:30:46.300
When you try to stop.

00:30:46.300 --> 00:30:47.670
And often, we put that off.

00:30:47.670 --> 00:30:50.860
We say, yeah, yeah, I could
stop if I wanted to.

00:30:50.860 --> 00:30:52.135
I just choose not to.

00:30:55.860 --> 00:31:00.930
So then my late 20s, I tried
to stop spending.

00:31:00.930 --> 00:31:03.310
I tried to stop shagging.

00:31:03.310 --> 00:31:05.220
I tried to stop getting high.

00:31:05.220 --> 00:31:06.470
All of these things.

00:31:06.470 --> 00:31:07.490
And I've got no program.

00:31:07.490 --> 00:31:09.560
I've got no idea how to do it.

