00:31:34.832 --> 00:31:36.840
The early '80s were great
for the band.

00:31:36.840 --> 00:31:39.400
The second half of the '80s,
we were hanging on.

00:31:39.400 --> 00:31:42.480
Hanging on like the fucking
zeitgeist was over there, and

00:31:42.480 --> 00:31:46.510
it was like, maybe you guys
should just call it a day.

00:31:46.510 --> 00:31:49.590
We were like, we were just
getting started.

00:31:49.590 --> 00:31:50.980
